  "title": "Audit Seniors",
  "description": "<p><strong>AUDIT SENIORS</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p>· Provide statutory audit services and compilation of financial statements and to assist in other and special assignments.</p>\n<p>· Plan engagements, audit strategies and to perform audit procedures and related works in compliance with Singapore Auditing and Financial Reporting Standards with guidance and supervision from managers and partners.</p>\n<p>· Develop and maintain long-term client relationship.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>· Candidates must be suitably qualified with at least Diploma/Advanced Diplomas/ Bachelor’s Degree in Accounting, Finance or professional qualifications recognized by ISCA</p>\n<p>· At least 2 to 3 years of related working experience</p>\n<p>· Excellent analytical, verbal and written communication skills both English and Mandarin (in order to liaise with Mandarin speaking associates)</p>\n<p>· Sound knowledge of Singapore Auditing and Financial Reporting Standards</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Why Join Us</strong></p>\n<p>The Firm recognizes and acknowledges that the quality of our people are the key drivers to the Firm success and hence, the Firm is constantly on the look-out for dedicated and committed professionals to grow with the Firm.</p>\n<p>In attracting, retaining and motivating our people the Firm endeavor in providing a continuous learning environment in equipping our people with the necessary skills that help the Firm in fully developing our people potentials and professional growth.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>If you have what it takes:-</strong></p>\n<p>Please email/send your comprehensive resume, including a recent photograph and to include the following details:-</p>\n<p>1. Reasons for leaving current employment</p>\n<p>2. Availability / Notice period required</p>\n<p>3. Last drawn/ current and expected salary</p>\n<p>4. References (if any)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>The Recruitment Partner</strong></p>\n<p><strong>ACFOSS PAC</strong></p>\n<p>100D Pasir Panjang Road #02-11</p>\n<p>Meissa</p>\n<p>Singapore 118520</p>\n<p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:hr@acfoss.com.sg\"><strong>hr@acfoss.com.sg</strong></a></p>\n<p>Website : www.acfoss.com.sg</p>\n<p><em>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified</em></p>",
